Subject: head leak

On my 79 2.0l GE engine, I lapped the cylinders to the heads with lapping 
compound and left out the metal shim, torqued both heads correctly and both 
heads leaked.  I removed both heads, put the metal shims between the 
cylinders and the head and all leaks stopped.  gt
